sequenceDiagram
    participant user
    participant browser
    participant server

    user->>browser: Enters note text and clicks Save
    Note right of browser: JavaScript intercepts form submit\n(prevents default page reload)

    browser->>browser: Create note object\n(add date + content)
    browser->>server: POST /exampleapp/new_note_spa\n(JSON data)
    activate server

    Note right of server: Server validates and stores\nnew note in memory/database

    server-->>browser: 201 Created\n(Returns created note as JSON)
    deactivate server

    Note right of browser: JavaScript updates notes list\nin the DOM dynamically
